Release Notes
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
VirtualDJ is a DJ software for PC and MAC. It is used by DJs to replace their
turntables and CD players, and use digital music instead of vinyl and CDs. In
the same way that the CD players used by DJs have more options than a regular Hi-Fi CD player, VirtualDJ has more options than a simple media player like
iTunes.
